title: Grateful Dead Live at Civic Arena on 1973-09-24
description:
Set 1

Promised Land, Sugaree, Jack Straw, They Love Each Other, Mexicali Blues, Loose Lucy, Looks Like Rain, Row Jimmy, Big River, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Around & Around

Set 2

Ramble On Rose, El Paso, Mississippi Half Step, Greatest Story Ever Told, China Doll, Truckin'-> Maybe You Know-> Eyes Of The World*-> Weather Report Suite Prelude*-> Weather Report Suite Part 1*-> Let It Grow*, Sugar Magnolia

*with Martin Fiero and Joe Ellis on horns. Merry-Go-Round Broke Down' tuning before 'Greatest'. Doug Sahm opened
